## Design Variants

The following variant axes control the component's visual appearance:

### Size → use prop `size`

- `X-Small` **(default)**
- `Small`
- `Medium`
- `Large`
- `X-Large`

### Expanded → use prop `expanded`

- `True`
- `False` **(default)**

### Chevron → use prop `chevronPosition`

- `Left` **(default)**
- `Right`
- `Split`

### Blue signifier

- `False` **(default)**
- `True`

### Additional Design Controls

| Control | Type | Default | Description |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| Signifier label | text | Signifier | * Signifier label is additional text control for AccordionItem header. |
| Title | text | Accordion | - |
| Signifier | boolean | true | * Signifier label is additional text control for AccordionItem header. |
| Left Icon | boolean | false | - |
| ↳ Icon | instance_swap | 132354:9710 | - |

